msgid "Scenario VIII: Return to Shattered Aeons"
msgstr "冒险VIII：重返破碎永世"

msgid "Create the exploration deck. This is done by taking the 4 single-sided [[Otherworld]] locations. Do not include any of the other encounter cards listed in the original setup instructions."
msgstr "构建探索牌堆。将4张单面的[[异界]]地点混洗形成探索牌堆，不要加入原版的冒险设置指示中列出的其他遭遇卡。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: Formless Spawn, Relic of Ages (Unleash the Timestream), A Pocket in Time, Act 4a—“Paradise Lost”, Act 4a—“Timelock”, and all of the single-sided [[Shattered]] locations."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：无形之子、古代遗物<i>(时光涌流)</i>、时间之窗、场景4a—“失乐园”、场景4a—“锁定时间”、所有的单面[[破碎]]地点。"

msgid "For the duration of this scenario, the following additional rule applies:"
msgstr "在本场冒险期间，增加以下额外规则："
